...adding onto that, I‚Äôm generally a very picky rater. ¬†I start a movie off at 2.5 stars (average) and then bump it up or down based on how I felt about it. ¬†5-stars is reserved for a small selection of movies that truly shook me to my core and had a big impact on me in some regard.
